item.title: 3d print project, lampshade
item.description: A couple of weeks ago I gave myself a 3d print for a present. üòù I opted for a Creality Ender 3 pro and order it from Ali Express. With the first print I was amazed how good the quality now is on these budget printers. My last experience with 3d printing was about 10 years ago and the quality was quite different then on budget printers. So I am quite happy with this printer.
